detail_desc: Wide jumper in a soft, rib-knit cashmere blend with a double-layered turtle neck, gently dropped shoulders and long sleeves.
Jumper knitted in soft cashmere with a round neck, long raglan sleeves and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Cable-knit jumper in a soft wool blend containing some alpaca. Wide fit at the top and fitted to the hem with wide ribbing. Wide sleeves with narrow ribbed cuffs.

STUDIO COLLECTION. Cropped, boxy-style jumper in a loose, chunky, crocheted cotton blend. V-neck, low dropped shoulders and long, wide sleeves that taper to the cuffs. The jumper is heavy and should be stored flat to retain its shape.
STUDIO COLLECTION. Short jumper knitted in a wool and cashmere blend with a stand-up collar and textured-knit shoulder sections. Visible, decorative stitching at the front, back and hem.
Rib-knit jumper in wool containing some cashmere. V-neck, extra-long, wide raglan sleeves, high slits in the sides and elasticated ribbing at the cuffs and hem. Longer at the back.
Jumper in a soft, chunky-knit alpaca blend with a fluffy finish. High, ribbed collar, a zip at the top, dropped shoulders and long sleeves with sewn-in turn-ups.
Oversized top in sweatshirt fabric made from a cotton and silk blend with a slight sheen. Dropped shoulders, long sleeves and ribbing around the neckline and cuffs.
Jumper knitted in soft cashmere. Short raglan sleeves with ribbed trims and ribbing around the neckline and hem.
Short-sleeved jumper in soft, fine-knit cashmere with a ribbed collar, V-neck and ribbed trims around the sleeves and hem.

Oversized cardigan in a wool knit with decorative seams in a contrasting colour, low dropped shoulders and wide, long sleeves. V-neck, buttons down the front and wide ribbing around the neckline, down the button band and at the cuffs and hem.
Jumper knitted in soft cashmere. Short raglan sleeves with ribbed trims and ribbing around the neckline and hem.
Jumper knitted in soft cashmere with a round neck, long raglan sleeves and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Jumper knitted in a merino wool and cashmere blend with a ribbed stand-up collar and zip at the top. Long sleeves with elbow patches, and ribbing at the cuffs and hem.
STUDIO COLLECTION. Wide, polo-neck jumper in a wool knit with dropped shoulders and straight, extra-long sleeves. Twisted seams at the front to create a tapered silhouette, and an asymmetric hem.
Rib-knit jumper in wool containing some cashmere. V-neck, extra-long, wide raglan sleeves, high slits in the sides and elasticated ribbing at the cuffs and hem. Longer at the back.
Oversized top in sweatshirt fabric made from a cotton and silk blend with a slight sheen. Dropped shoulders, long sleeves and ribbing around the neckline and cuffs.

STUDIO COLLECTION. Jumper in a soft, fine-knit wool blend containing some cashmere with contrasting colour flatlock seams and vertical seams front and back. Ribbed stand-up collar, ribbing at the cuffs and hem, and high slits in the sides.
Jumper knitted in soft cashmere. Short raglan sleeves with ribbed trims and ribbing around the neckline and hem.
Fitted jumper in soft, fine-knit, ribbed cashmere with 3/4-length sleeves and ribbing around the neckline.
